ihu.com/question/31042779\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zhihu.com%2Fquestion%2F31042779&d=h2ujG81d2RzhzrPyGMgS1J7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=027f1e8c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.zhihu.com/question/31042779</a><br />\n<br />\n越南買到既俄羅斯軍火，係先進過曬支那買既俄羅斯軍火n個世代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同時越南想買埋美國既作戰潛艇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d8a6d1639a9a1df941133fda42b7cd40f8d2941","tid":358644,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T07:38:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不如泊香港啦，可以索料</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港咪又係要中國左批又批"},{"pid":"b7ad40302e8c6d0b5732b422b5aa4be1b9d04479","tid":358644,"uid":21035,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T07:45:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不如泊香港啦，可以索料</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港咪又係要中國左批又批</blockquote><br />\n到佢唔批咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6b91fbe33595f2ed401b98d7678387095fc583f","tid":358644,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T08:17:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>那片白樺林<br />\n俄羅斯留學諮詢，俄語預科，入系考試諮詢與輔導<br />\n<br />\n從冷戰開始越南和蘇聯的關係一直不錯，現在的關係更是進入蜜月期。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯的關鍵利益所在：<br />\n1.俄羅斯軍售<br />\n2.核電站建設<br />\n3.南海油氣資源開發<br />\n4.牽制中國，或者說對中國勢力進入中亞的反制。<br />\n<br />\n越南的關鍵利益所在：<br />\n1.吸引俄羅斯遊客<br />\n2.勞動密集型產品出口俄羅斯，在中低端市場與中國產品有激烈的競爭。（在莫斯科批發市場會經常遇到越南人）<br />\n3.利用俄羅斯的力量（南海油氣，俄羅斯先進軍備）牽制中國<br />\n4.滿足能源需求，值得一提的是越南現在還從中國進口電力。<br />\n5.獲取先進技術。<br />\n<br />\n由此觀之，雙方的利益契合度很高，導致雙方的文化交流需求加強，越南人學習俄語也是情理之中的事了。<br />\n值得一提的是在俄羅斯越南留學生大部分都是公費生，學霸很多。<br />\n<br />\n為什麼那麼多越南人學俄語？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/31042779\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zhihu.com%2Fquestion%2F31042779&d=h2ujG81d2RzhzrPyGMgS1J7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=027f1e8c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.zhihu.com/question/31042779</a><br />\n<br />\n越南買到既俄羅斯軍火，係先進過曬支那買既俄羅斯軍火n個世代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同時越南想買埋美國既作戰潛艇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然俄羅斯都照賣最先進既俄製軍火俾越南, 但俄羅斯對南海既態度都係左搖右罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以長遠利講越南與印度都係搵美國更實際同更保險.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c8f0d2d623317a7b5064f58328aa71c85443c80","tid":358644,"uid":100986,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T08:29:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>不如泊香港啦，可以索料</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港咪又係要中國左批又批</blockquote><br />\n到佢唔批咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\ntrump到而家都仲未肯批美國艦隊同航母停泊台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3258cb186ca7cd2ea8ddcf9a02e7c35a6f9b52a","tid":358644,"uid":5220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T08:55:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>不如泊香港啦，可以索料</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港咪又係要中國左批又批</blockquote><br />\n到佢唔批咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以唔批<br />\n不過回程時會經過台灣海峽啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"161bba077cb819ba2e44eef5fcc7f07778f2232b","tid":358644,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T15:13:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>不如泊香港啦，可以索料</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港咪又係要中國左批又批</blockquote><br />\n到佢唔批咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以唔批<br />\n不過回程時會經過台灣海峽啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b584bd2083e0cb366aff842bfb8f2eafc19d78b9","tid":358644,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime